detail_desc: Ankle-length jeans in washed stretch denim with fake front pockets, real back pockets and tapered legs. Wide jersey ribbing at the waist for best fit.
Metal and plastic hair clips in various sizes and designs. Length from 6.8 cm to 10.2 cm.
Long-sleeved dress in woven fabric with a round neckline, an opening and button at the back of the neck and a smocked seam at the waist. Unlined.
Blouse in an airy weave with a wide neckline and smocking front and back. Long puff sleeves with smocked sections over the elbows and narrow elastication at the cuffs.

Padded jacket in windproof, water-repellent, breathable functional fabric with folded seams and reflective details. Detachable hood, stand-up collar and a zip down the front with a jersey chin guard. Patch front pockets with a flap and hook and loop fastening and long sleeves with an adjustable hook and loop tab and inner ribbing at the cuffs. Longer and rounded at the back. Recycled polyester lining and filling. The jacket has a water-repellent coating without fluorocarbons.
Soft, non-wired lace bras in lace with mesh-lined cups with removable inserts. Narrow adjustable shoulder straps, elastication under the bust and a wide lace hem. No fasteners.
Shorts in organic cotton sweatshirt fabric with covered elastication and a decorative drawstring at the waist.
Fitted top in ribbed jersey with a deep neckline and long sleeves.
Socks in a soft, fine-knit cotton blend with elasticated tops.

Ankle-length cigarette trousers in a stretch cotton blend with a zip fly, concealed hook-and-eye fasteners and a regular waist with concealed elastication. Side pockets, fake welt back pockets and tapered legs with creases.
Fully lined bikini. Flounced top with narrow shoulder straps, one with a small metal decoration, and a plastic fastener at the back. Bottoms with a decorative bow at each side.
Double-layer hat in patterned jersey.
Fancy dress costume with a zip down the front, hood with appliqués and ribbing at the cuffs and hems.
Short, A-line skirt with a high waist and buttons down the front.

Oversized, knee-length shirt jacket in grained imitation leather with a pointed collar, buttons down the front and yoke with a pleat at the back. Low dropped shoulders, long, wide sleeves with wide, buttoned cuffs, large open chest pockets and a rounded hem. Longer at the back. Unlined.
Shaftless socks in thin cotton jersey with elastication at the top to hold them in place.
Scarf in a soft weave with fringes along the short sides.
Jumper in a soft rib knit containing some wool with long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem. The polyester content of the jumper is recycled.
Long-sleeved tops in soft jersey. The cotton content of the tops is organic.
Short dress in airy, spotted mesh with short, flounce-trimmed sleeves, a frill-trimmed yoke and seam with a flounce at the hem. Jersey underdress.
Short top in sweatshirt fabric with a ribbed turtle neck, dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.

Straight-cut blouse in a softly draping silk and viscose weave with an opening and buttons at the back of the neck and yoke with a pleat. Long sleeves with wide buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem. Longer at the back.
Umbrella in transparent, printed plastic with a plastic handle. Length 77 cm.
Short dress in a softly draping weave with a collar, V-neck, concealed buttons down the front and a tie belt at the waist. Long sleeves, buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem. Unlined.
Fully lined bikini bottoms with a low waist and ties at the sides.
Hipster briefs in soft jersey made from a modal blend with a lace trim at the top. Mid waist, lined gusset, wide sides and medium coverage at the back.
Sleeveless, knee-length dress in woven fabric with a detachable belt at the waist with a covered metal buckle. Lined.
Jumper in a soft knit containing wool and mohair in a relaxed fit with low dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Long-sleeved top in sturdy, block-coloured cotton jersey. Panel with a text print down the sleeves, ribbing around the neckline and cuffs, and slits in the sides. Slightly longer at the back.
Top in printed sweatshirt fabric with a lined hood, long sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.

Long-sleeved top in sweatshirt fabric made from a cotton blend with a text print and reversible sequin motif on the front (sizes 1½-3Y with normal sequins). Jersey-lined hood with a wrapover front, and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Fine-knit socks in a soft cotton blend with high shafts and elasticated tops.
Large hoop earrings made of rigid metal chain. Diameter 5 cm.
Jersey top with a slightly wider neckline and long dolman sleeves.
Full-length leggings in sturdy jersey made from a Tencel™ lyocell blend. High waist with concealed elastication, sewn-in creases down the front and back and a concealed zip at the front of the hems.
Shorts in a checked weave with an extended waistband, zip fly and hook-and-eye fastening. Welt side pockets, fake back pockets and sewn-in turn-ups at the hems.
Body in stretch lace with a crocheted look. Jersey-lined cups with a scalloped trim, narrow, adjustable shoulder straps and press-studs at the crotch.
Short dress in patterned satin with narrow adjustable shoulder straps and sewn-in cups with side support. Concealed zip at the back, a seam at the waist and a gently flared skirt. Lined.

Push-up triangle bikini top with moulded, padded cups for a larger bust and fuller cleavage. Narrow, adjustable shoulder straps that can be fastened straight or crossed at the back. Adjustable hook-and-eye fastening at the back.
Headband in a soft knit containing some wool with a draped detail at the front. Width approx. 11.5 cm.
Short-sleeved jumper in a soft knit containing some wool with a collar and button placket. Rib trims around the sleeves and wide ribbing at the hem.

Small shoulder bag in glittery imitation leather with embroidery on the front and appliqués at the top. Narrow shoulder strap with a press-stud at one end, a zip at the top and a hanger at one side. Lined. Size approx. 3.5x10.5x15 cm.
Blouse in an airy cotton weave with a round neck and small opening with buttons at the front. Short cap sleeves, broderie anglaise frills at the top and a gathered seam at the chest.
Jumper in a soft rib knit containing some wool with dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Short jumper in a soft knit with embroidery, long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.

Imitation suede espadrilles with pointed toes, a braided jute trim around the soles and an adjustable imitation leather ankle strap with a metal buckle. Imitation leather insoles, satin linings and rubber soles.
Short skirt in woven fabric with a high, frill-trimmed elasticated waist and side pockets. Unlined.
Jumper in a soft knit. Relaxed fit with long, raglan balloon sleeves, ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem, and slits in the sides. Slightly longer at the back.
Straight-cut jacket in a striped weave with notch lapels, buttons at the front and welt front pockets with a flap. Decorative buttons at the cuffs. Lined.
Top in organic cotton jersey and a pair of culottes in viscose jersey. Top with short sleeves and a tie detail at the hem. Culottes with elasticated smocking at the waist.
Boys’ briefs in soft cotton jersey with an elasticated waist and lined front.
Multi-strand necklace of thin metal chains in various designs. One chain decorated with plastic beads and one with a round pendant. Adjustable length 40-47 cm.
Top in sweatshirt fabric with a hood and long sleeves with ribbed cuffs.

Short dress in a crêpe weave with a round neckline and an opening with a button at the back of the neck. Smocked seam under the bust and long, wide sleeves with smocking and a small frill trim at the cuffs. Unlined.
Hooded coat in a slightly crêped weave with a concealed, double-breasted press-stud fastening and side pockets. Tie belt at the waist and an asymmetric hem with a single back vent. Unlined.
Short, fitted jersey top with short sleeves and a visible seam down the front. Slightly shorter front with a knot detail at the hem.
Knee-length shorts in a patterned cotton weave with an elasticated, drawstring waist, fake fly, side pockets and a welt back pocket.
T-shirts in soft jersey. The cotton content of the T-shirts is organic.
Cardigan in soft, fluffy pile with long sleeves and no buttons. Jersey lining.
Hole-knitted jumper with a wide, frill-trimmed neckline with lacing and an opening at the top. Long sleeves with ribbing and a frill trim at the cuffs, and wide ribbing at the hem.
Polo-neck jumper in fine-knit premium cotton with ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Top in patterned cotton jersey with a narrow ribbed trim around the neckline and short cap sleeves. Rounded and longer at the back.

Shell trousers in wind- and waterproof, breathable functional fabric with folded seams, elasticated hems and a reinforced elastic strap under the feet. Detachable, adjustable elastic braces. Lined. The trousers have a water-repellent coating without fluorocarbons.
Scarf in soft, rib-knit cashmere.
T-shirt in jersey made from a cotton blend with an interactive motif.
Joggers in soft, organic cotton jersey with an elasticated waist, pockets in the side seams and ribbed hems.
Leather loafers with pointed toes and a tab across the front. Leather linings and insoles and rubber soles. Heel 3.5 cm.
Push-up bra in lace and mesh with underwired, padded cups for a larger bust and fuller cleavage. Adjustable shoulder straps and a hook-and-eye fastening at the back.

Set with a long-sleeved top and pair of joggers in soft, block-coloured sweatshirt fabric. Top with a press-stud on one shoulder and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem. Joggers with an elasticated drawstring waist and ribbed hems. Soft brushed inside.
Large elastic scrunchie in velour.
Dance shoes in imitation leather with a glittery elastic panel over the foot. Cotton linings and insoles and soft suede soles.
Seersucker dress in a narrow cut at the top with a gentle flare to the hem. Elasticated top, narrow shoulder straps and a rounded hem.
Short dress in a patterned viscose weave with a V-neck, wrapover front with ties at the waist and short sleeves.

Blouse in a softly draping weave with a round neck and small opening at the back with a concealed button at the back of the neck. Gathered seams on the shoulders, long batwing sleeves with buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem.
Short top in sweatshirt fabric with a high, ribbed stand-up collar with a zip at the front. Dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside.
Elasticated hairbands with appliqués.
Fully lined swimsuit with a deep V-neck at the front, cups with removable inserts and ties that fasten at the back of the neck.
Hooded jacket in lightweight sweatshirt fabric with a zip down the front, front pockets and ribbing at the cuffs and hem.
Fine-knit socks in a soft cotton blend with a ribbed, embroidered shaft.
Top in an airy weave with spaghetti shoulder straps, a lace-trimmed V-neck and buttons at the top. Seam with a flounce at the hem.
